{{short description| A breathing gas mixed from helium and oxygen }}
{{about|the breathing gas|the cryogenic system|Heliox (cryogenic equipment)}}
{{Infobox drug
| drug_name          = Heliox
| CAS_number = 58933-55-4 
| PubChem            = 123812
| chemical_formula   = HeO<sub>2</sub>
| molecular_weight   = 36.001
